Class SemanticAnnotationProperties

org.odpi.openmetadata.frameworks.openmetadata.properties.surveyreports.SemanticAnnotationProperties
public class SemanticAnnotationProperties extends DataFieldAnnotationProperties
SemanticAnnotationProperties provides a recommendation as to the likely meaning of data. This can be expressed informally with explicit strings, or via lists of GUIDs that match elements in a formal glossary. It can be attached to an asset or a data field within an asset.
